import React, {useState} from 'react'
import {Form, Button} from 'react-bootstrap'
import axios from 'axios'

const RegistrationScreen = () => {
    let studentID, changeID = useState('')  
    let firstName, changeFirstName = useState('')  
    let lastName, changeLastName = useState('') 
    let email, changeEmail = useState('')
    let phoneNumber, changePhoneNumber = useState('')
    let gradYear, changeGradYear = useState('')

    
    const onSubmit = (e) =>{
        e.preventDefault()
        try{
            axios.post('http://localhost:7777', {
                headers: {"studentID": studentID, "firstName": firstName, }
            })
        }

        catch (e){
            console.log(e)
        }
        
    } 
    return (
        <Form>
            <Form.Group controlId="formBasicText">
                <Form.Label>Student ID</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control value="studentID" type="text" placeholder="Enter ID" required/>
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group controlId="formBasicText">
                <Form.Label>First Name</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control value="firstName" type="text" placeholder="Enter Name" required/>
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group controlId="formBasicText">
                <Form.Label>Last Name</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control value="lastName" type="text" placeholder="Enter Name" required/>
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group controlId="formBasicEmail">
                <Form.Label>Email address</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control value="email" type="email" placeholder="Enter email" required/>
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group controlId="formBasicText">
                <Form.Label>Phone Number (optional)</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control value="phoneNumber" type="text" placeholder="Phone Number"/>
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group controlId="RegistrationForm.ControlSelect1">
                <Form.Label>Graduation Year</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control as="select" value="gradYear">
                    <option>2021</option>
                    <option>2022</option>
                    <option>2023</option>
                    <option>2024</option>
                </Form.Control>
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group>
                <Form.Label>Do you have any experience with Cybersecurity? (Experience Not Required)</Form.Label>
                <Form.Check type="radio" name="radios" label="Yes" value="yes" id="formExperienceYes"/>         
                <Form.Check type="radio" name="radios" label="No" value="no" id="formExperienceNo"/>
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group controlId="RegistrationForm.ControlTextarea1">
                <Form.Label>If you answered yes to the previous question, please elaborate on your experience (what you have learned)</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control value="memberExperience" as="textarea" rows={6}/>
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group controlId="RegistrationForm.ControlTextarea2">
                <Form.Label>Why do you want to join the Security Ops Club?</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control value="reasonJoin" as="textarea" rows={6} required/>
            </Form.Group>
            <Button variant="primary" size="lg" type="submit" onClick={onSubmit}>
                Register
            </Button>
        </Form>
    )
}

export default RegistrationScreen
